                1. There are three types of 'Coordination':
                [list]
                [*] Pokémon Contests
                [*] Contest Spectaculars
                [*] Pokémon Showcases
                [/list]
                2. Two Ribbons are awarded at each Pokémon Contest.
                3. The Overall Winner automatically receives a ribbon and the runner-up receives ribbon; however, the runner-up must defend their position against the 3rd place coordinator (Once that person has been determined).
            {/slide}
